1. Benefit of vendle
   vim plugin manager that ease the work of manually copy/delete doc/.vim files to/from ~/.vim/doc and ~/.vim/plugin
2. install step
  1)git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle
  2)edit ~/.vimrc
  
  set nocompatible              " be iMproved

  set rtp+=~/.vim/bundle/vundle/
  call vundle#rc()

  " let Vundle manage Vundle
  " required!
  Bundle 'gmarik/vundle'
  3) in vim editor,type ":BundleInstall"
